description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=1/3, Mature Content=1/3. Finally the massage you've been waiting for is here! Stick Massage lets you massage any way you want to! Want a bit more "game" in your massage? Play Massage For Money and see how skilled you are. Want a more "hands off" approach? Use automatic mode and let the game do the massaging for you.
